---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="关于我" description="施施小洛——作家、出版策划人。策划出版多部超级畅销书，擅长挖掘新人、操盘千万级 IP，打造全产业链。">
    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-24">

        <!-- Hero: Portrait + Identity -->
        <header class="flex flex-col md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-20 items-center mb-24 md:mb-32">
            <div class="aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/portrait.jpg" alt="施施小洛肖像" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700">
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="text-brand-coral uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-medium mb-4">Writer · Publisher · Creator</p>
                <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl font-light leading-tight mb-8">施施小洛</h1>
                <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-light text-lg md:text-xl mb-6">
                    作家，出版策划人。<br/>
                    策划出版多部超级畅销书，累计销量过千万册。
                </p>
                <p class="text-stone-500 leading-relaxed font-light">
                    擅长挖掘新人作者、操盘千万级 IP、打造从内容到影视的全产业链。写过专栏，出过书，做过杂志，也当过幕后推手。
                </p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Career Timeline -->
        <section class="mb-24 md:mb-32">
            <p class="text-brand-coral uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-medium mb-12">Career</p>
            <div class="space-y-16">

                <!-- Block 1: 杂志时代 -->
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-12">
                    <div class="md:col-span-3">
                        <p class="font-serif text-stone-400 text-sm tracking-wide">杂志时代</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:col-span-9">
                        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl font-light mb-4">《今古传奇》·《悬疑世界》</h3>
                        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
                            从杂志编辑起步，深耕类型文学。在《今古传奇》和蔡骏主编的《悬疑世界》杂志，积累了对故事结构、读者心理和市场节奏的敏锐直觉。这段经历奠定了此后所有工作的底层能力——判断什么样的故事能打动人。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Block 2: 图书策划 -->
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-12">
                    <div class="md:col-span-3">
                        <p class="font-serif text-stone-400 text-sm tracking-wide">图书策划</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:col-span-9">
                        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl font-light mb-4">雁北堂 · 超级畅销书操盘手</h3>
                        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-light mb-6">
                            在雁北堂担任图书策划人期间，策划出版多部现象级畅销书。擅长从零开始挖掘素人作者，把一个灵感打磨成一本百万级销量的图书，再从图书延伸到影视、有声、周边的全产业链。
                        </p>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                            <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-coral pl-4">
                                <p class="font-serif text-lg mb-1">《桐花中路私立协济医院怪谈》</p>
                                <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">100 万 + 销量</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="border-l-2 border-stone-200 pl-4">
                                <p class="font-serif text-lg mb-1">《完美嫌疑人》</p>
                                <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">悬疑畅销系列</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Block 3: 专栏与写作 -->
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-12">
                    <div class="md:col-span-3">
                        <p class="font-serif text-stone-400 text-sm tracking-wide">写作</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:col-span-9">
                        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl font-light mb-4">专栏作家 · 独立写作者</h3>
                        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
                            不只做幕后。写过专栏，出过自己的书。从编辑到作者的身份切换，让我对「创作」有了双重理解——既知道一本好书怎么写出来，也知道它怎么被看见。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Block 4: 现在 -->
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-12">
                    <div class="md:col-span-3">
                        <p class="font-serif text-stone-400 text-sm tracking-wide">现在</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:col-span-9">
                        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl font-light mb-4">关系心理学 · 内容创作者</h3>
                        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
                            十几年出版经验之后，把目光转向了人与人之间最本质的课题——关系。用出版人的结构化思维，拆解亲密关系、自我觉察、女性成长中那些说不清道不明的东西。犀利，但有温度。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Core Strengths -->
        <section class="mb-24 md:mb-32">
            <p class="text-brand-coral uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-medium mb-12">What I Do</p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
                <div>
                    <p class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-brand-coral mb-3">01</p>
                    <h4 class="font-serif text-lg mb-3">挖掘新人</h4>
                    <p class="text-stone-500 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        从茫茫来稿中发现潜力作者，陪他们从第一本书走到畅销书。好编辑的价值，是让才华被看见。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-brand-coral mb-3">02</p>
                    <h4 class="font-serif text-lg mb-3">操盘 IP</h4>
                    <p class="text-stone-500 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        一本书不是终点。从图书到影视、有声、周边，把一个好故事的价值放到最大。操盘过千万级 IP 项目。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-brand-coral mb-3">03</p>
                    <h4 class="font-serif text-lg mb-3">全产业链</h4>
                    <p class="text-stone-500 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        内容策划、出版发行、版权运营、影视改编——从上游到下游，打通每一个环节。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Get In Touch -->
        <section class="mb-24 md:mb-32">
            <p class="text-brand-coral uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-medium mb-12">Get In Touch</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-brand-coral transition-colors">
                    <a href="https://weibo.com/u/1212058190" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mb-3">
                            <path d="M4 4c-.5 0-1 .5-1 1v4c0 4.4 3.6 8 8 8s8-3.6 8-8V5c0-.5-.5-1-1-1H4z"/>
                            <circle cx="12" cy="9" r="3"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="font-medium text-sm">微博</span>
                        <span class="text-stone-400 text-xs mt-1">@施施小洛</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-brand-coral transition-colors">
                    <a href="https://www.douyin.com/user/MS4wLjABAAAAoY28ptZFGhSHddr1nDoIkrd9m9ZXz3isP0sMC-4fSitMCCGeHz6OxVz4uJQx9EBe" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mb-3">
                            <path d="M17.5 12a5.5 5.5 0 1 1-5.5-5.5 5.5 0 0 1 5.5 5.5z"/>
                            <path d="M2 12v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H3a1 1 0 0 0-1 1z"/>
                            <path d="M17.5 12a5.5 5.5 0 1 1 0 11"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="font-medium text-sm">抖音·情感</span>
                        <span class="text-stone-400 text-xs mt-1">短视频</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-brand-coral transition-colors">
                    <a href="https://www.douyin.com/user/MS4wLjABAAAAwkB6ZdS0Jnhuwsx-bxddj7t2l64DTmCSY2-thLcFddc" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mb-3">
                            <path d="M17.5 12a5.5 5.5 0 1 1-5.5-5.5 5.5 0 0 1 5.5 5.5z"/>
                            <path d="M2 12v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H3a1 1 0 0 0-1 1z"/>
                            <path d="M17.5 12a5.5 5.5 0 1 1 0 11"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="font-medium text-sm">抖音·读书号</span>
                        <span class="text-stone-400 text-xs mt-1">生活分享</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-brand-coral transition-colors">
                    <a href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/user/profile/54e4cdbeb4c4d674d0bed215" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mb-3">
                            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
                            <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/>
                            <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="font-medium text-sm">小红书</span>
                        <span class="text-stone-400 text-xs mt-1">@施施小洛</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-brand-coral transition-colors">
                    <a href="https://space.bilibili.com/395457409" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mb-3">
                            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                            <path d="M7 7h10M7 12h4m7 0h-2"/>
                            <path d="M7 17h10"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="font-medium text-sm">B站</span>
                        <span class="text-stone-400 text-xs mt-1">@施施小洛</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-brand-coral transition-colors cursor-pointer" data-qr-trigger="wechat">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mb-3">
                            <path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="font-medium text-sm">公众号</span>
                        <span class="text-stone-400 text-xs mt-1">施施小洛</span>
                        <span class="text-brand-coral text-[10px] mt-1">点击查看二维码</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-brand-coral transition-colors cursor-pointer" data-qr-trigger="channels">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mb-3">
                            <polygon points="23 7 16 12 23 17 23 7"/>
                            <rect x="1" y="5" width="15" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="font-medium text-sm">视频号</span>
                        <span class="text-stone-400 text-xs mt-1">施施小洛</span>
                        <span class="text-brand-coral text-[10px] mt-1">点击查看二维码</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Services -->
        <section class="mb-24 md:mb-32">
            <p class="text-brand-coral uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-medium mb-12">Services</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-brand-coral transition-colors">
                    <h4 class="font-serif text-lg mb-2">看大纲 / 看稿</h4>
                    <p class="text-brand-coral font-medium text-sm mb-3">¥800 / 万字（大纲 ¥500 起）</p>
                    <p class="text-stone-500 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        资深编辑视角，帮你把握故事结构、节奏和市场方向。适合长篇小说、非虚构稿件。
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-brand-coral transition-colors">
                    <h4 class="font-serif text-lg mb-2">看剧本</h4>
                    <p class="text-brand-coral font-medium text-sm mb-3">¥1,500 起</p>
                    <p class="text-stone-500 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        从故事逻辑到影视化可行性，给出专业意见。十年出版+影视改编经验背书。
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-brand-coral transition-colors">
                    <h4 class="font-serif text-lg mb-2">读书 / 关系心理学咨询</h4>
                    <p class="text-brand-coral font-medium text-sm mb-3">¥400 / 小时（首次 ¥299）</p>
                    <p class="text-stone-500 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        亲密关系、自我觉察、情绪管理、阅读疗愈。犀利但有温度的一对一对话。
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-brand-coral transition-colors">
                    <h4 class="font-serif text-lg mb-2">写作辅导</h4>
                    <p class="text-brand-coral font-medium text-sm mb-3">¥2,000 / 4 次课（单次 ¥600）</p>
                    <p class="text-stone-500 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        从灵感到成稿的全程陪跑。适合想出书、写专栏、做自媒体的你。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Book a Consultation -->
        <section class="mb-24 md:mb-32">
            <p class="text-brand-coral uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-medium mb-12">Book a Consultation</p>
            <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
                <form id="consultation-form" class="space-y-6">
                    <div>
                        <label for="name" class="text-stone-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block">姓名</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required class="w-full border border-stone-200 rounded px-4 py-3 text-sm font-light focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-coral transition-colors bg-white">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <label for="contact" class="text-stone-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block">联系方式</label>
                        <input type="text" id="contact" name="contact" required placeholder="微信号 / 手机号 / 邮箱" class="w-full border border-stone-200 rounded px-4 py-3 text-sm font-light focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-coral transition-colors bg-white">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <label for="service" class="text-stone-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block">服务类型</label>
                        <select id="service" name="service" class="w-full border border-stone-200 rounded px-4 py-3 text-sm font-light focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-coral transition-colors bg-white">
                            <option value="">请选择服务类型</option>
                            <option value="看大纲/看稿">看大纲/看稿</option>
                            <option value="看剧本">看剧本</option>
                            <option value="读书/关系心理学咨询">读书 / 关系心理学咨询</option>
                            <option value="写作辅导">写作辅导</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <label for="budget" class="text-stone-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block">预算</label>
                        <select id="budget" name="budget" class="w-full border border-stone-200 rounded px-4 py-3 text-sm font-light focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-coral transition-colors bg-white">
                            <option value="">请选择预算范围</option>
                            <option value="¥1,000 以内">¥1,000 以内</option>
                            <option value="¥1,000-3,000">¥1,000-3,000</option>
                            <option value="¥3,000-5,000">¥3,000-5,000</option>
                            <option value="¥5,000 以上">¥5,000 以上</option>
                            <option value="面议">面议</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <label for="description" class="text-stone-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block">项目描述</label>
                        <textarea id="description" name="description" rows="4" placeholder="简要描述您的项目或咨询需求" class="w-full border border-stone-200 rounded px-4 py-3 text-sm font-light focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-coral transition-colors bg-white"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    
                    <button type="submit" id="submit-btn" class="w-full bg-brand-coral text-white py-3 rounded font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
                        提交预约
                    </button>
                    <div id="form-message" class="mt-3 text-center text-sm min-h-[1.5em]"></div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <section class="border-t border-stone-200 pt-16">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                    <img src="/images/wechat-qr.jpg" alt="施施小洛公众号二维码" class="w-36 h-36 object-contain mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-light mb-2">关注公众号</h3>
                    <p class="text-stone-500 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        关系心理学、女性成长、出版圈观察。<br/>犀利洞察 + 实用建议，每天一篇。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                    <img src="/images/channels-qr.jpg" alt="施施小洛视频号二维码" class="w-36 h-36 object-contain mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-light mb-2">关注视频号</h3>
                    <p class="text-stone-500 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        短视频分享思考与生活点滴。<br/>扫码关注，不错过每一期更新。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- QR Modal -->
        <div id="qr-modal" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden items-center justify-center bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm" role="dialog" aria-modal="true">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-xs w-full mx-4 text-center shadow-xl relative">
                <button id="qr-modal-close" class="absolute top-3 right-3 text-stone-400 hover:text-stone-600 transition-colors" aria-label="关闭">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
                </button>
                <img id="qr-modal-img" src="" alt="" class="w-48 h-48 object-contain mx-auto mb-4" />
                <p id="qr-modal-title" class="font-serif text-lg"></p>
                <p id="qr-modal-desc" class="text-stone-400 text-sm mt-1"></p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>
    
    <script>
        // QR Modal
        const qrModal = document.getElementById('qr-modal')!;
        const qrImg = document.getElementById('qr-modal-img') as HTMLImageElement;
        const qrTitle = document.getElementById('qr-modal-title')!;
        const qrDesc = document.getElementById('qr-modal-desc')!;
        const qrClose = document.getElementById('qr-modal-close')!;

        const qrData: Record<string, { src: string; alt: string; title: string; desc: string }> = {
            wechat: { src: '/images/wechat-qr.jpg', alt: '施施小洛公众号二维码', title: '关注公众号「施施小洛」', desc: '微信扫码关注' },
            channels: { src: '/images/channels-qr.jpg', alt: '施施小洛视频号二维码', title: '关注视频号「施施小洛」', desc: '微信扫码关注' },
        };

        function openQrModal(type: string) {
            const d = qrData[type];
            if (!d) return;
            qrImg.src = d.src;
            qrImg.alt = d.alt;
            qrTitle.textContent = d.title;
            qrDesc.textContent = d.desc;
            qrModal.classList.remove('hidden');
            qrModal.classList.add('flex');
        }

        function closeQrModal() {
            qrModal.classList.add('hidden');
            qrModal.classList.remove('flex');
        }

        document.querySelectorAll('[data-qr-trigger]').forEach(el => {
            el.addEventListener('click', () => {
                const type = (el as HTMLElement).dataset.qrTrigger!;
                openQrModal(type);
            });
        });

        qrClose.addEventListener('click', closeQrModal);
        qrModal.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            if (e.target === qrModal) closeQrModal();
        });
        document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
            if (e.key === 'Escape' && !qrModal.classList.contains('hidden')) closeQrModal();
        });

        // Consultation Form
        const form = document.getElementById('consultation-form');
        const submitBtn = document.getElementById('submit-btn') as HTMLButtonElement;
        const formMessage = document.getElementById('form-message')!;

        form?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
            e.preventDefault();

            submitBtn.disabled = true;
            submitBtn.textContent = '提交中...';
            formMessage.textContent = '';
            formMessage.className = 'mt-3 text-center text-sm min-h-[1.5em]';

            try {
                const fd = new FormData(form);
                const res = await fetch('/api/consult', {
                    method: 'POST',
                    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                    body: JSON.stringify({
                        name: fd.get('name'),
                        contact: fd.get('contact'),
                        service: fd.get('service'),
                        budget: fd.get('budget'),
                        description: fd.get('description'),
                    }),
                });
                const data = await res.json();

                if (res.ok && data.success) {
                    formMessage.textContent = '✓ 已提交，我会尽快联系您';
                    formMessage.className = 'mt-3 text-center text-sm text-green-600 min-h-[1.5em]';
                    form.reset();
                } else {
                    throw new Error(data.error || '提交失败');
                }
            } catch {
                formMessage.textContent = '提交失败，请直接添加微信联系';
                formMessage.className = 'mt-3 text-center text-sm text-red-600 min-h-[1.5em]';
            } finally {
                submitBtn.disabled = false;
                submitBtn.textContent = '提交预约';
            }
        });
    </script>
</Layout>
